<p><a href="#sdfootnote51anc" name="sdfootnote51sym">51</a> There is an excerpt of the film on YouTube uploaded by Concord Media (the film’s distributor) with permission from the copyright holder. The film can be purchased as a DVD from Concord <a href="http://www.concordmedia.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.concordmedia.org.uk</a>. It can also be purchased and rented via Vimeo. All information is on the Concord website where teaching notes for the film can be found.</p>
